data.descriptionHtml:
Product name in Arabic: Drinkmate CO2 Cylinder (Refill/Exchange) Product name in English: Drinkmate CO2 Cylinder Refill/Exchange Brand: Drinkmate

Product description and benefits:
Pure food-grade gas: Drinkmate cylinders come filled with pure food-grade carbon dioxide (CO2) gas, ensuring you have healthy, sparkling drinks with the best taste.

Uninterrupted continuity: Keeping extra cylinders at home ensures you never stop making your favorite drinks when your current cylinder runs out.

Flexible replacement system: You can easily replace your empty cylinder with a new, full one, making the process economical and environmentally friendly.

Global safety standards: The cylinder is made of durable, high-quality aluminum in accordance with US Department of Transportation (US DOT) standards, ensuring maximum safety during use and storage.

Wide compatibility: Designed to work efficiently with Drinkmate machines and most home soda makers that use screw-in cylinders.

Technical specifications:
Material: Lightweight, durable aluminum.

Gas type: Carbon dioxide (CO2) intended for food and beverages.

Capacity: Enough to prepare up to 60 liters of carbonated drinks (depending on the chosen level of fizzing).

Standards: Compliant with international safety and security specifications (DOT).

Why do you need an extra cylinder?
To avoid unexpected interruptions, we always recommend having at least one spare cylinder. When your first cylinder runs out, you can immediately add the spare and continue preparing your drinks, then easily replace the empty one with a full one at a discounted price. This method ensures you consistently save money and always enjoy fresh soda.
data.title: DrinkMate CO2 Cylinder Refill (60L Cylinder Replacement)

data.descriptionHtml:
Product name in Arabic: DrinkMate 60L CO2 Carbonation Cylinder - For Soft Drinks
Product name in English: DrinkMate CO2 Carbonating Cylinder (Filled) 60L
Product description and benefits:
â¢ Manufacturing up to 60 bottles of soft drinks
â¢ Compatible with all Drinkmate and SodaStream machines in the Americas
â¢ Each cylinder comes fully charged
Technical specifications:
Type: 60-liter carbonization cylinder
Material: High-temperature resistant metal structure
A brief explanation of the general properties:
The single 60-liter carbonation cylinder allows you to produce a handful of bottles of fizzy drinks, and is compatible with all Drinkmate and SodaStream machines.
